BT /F1 11.00 Tf 0.120 0.120 0.140 rg 1 0 0 1 72.00 754.00 Tm (entity. And finally the Database stores and retrieves the real data.) Tj ET
BT /F1 11.00 Tf 0.120 0.120 0.140 rg 1 0 0 1 72.00 733.80 Tm (Think of it like a restaurant. The waiter is the controller - takes your order, never cooks. The chef is) Tj ET
