BT /F1 10.50 Tf 0.120 0.120 0.140 rg 1 0 0 1 72.00 151.40 Tm (Be honest about the trade-off, as the slide notes - it shows maturity and stops them over-using) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.50 Tf 0.120 0.120 0.140 rg 1 0 0 1 72.00 137.00 Tm (microservices: they add network calls, distributed data, and operational complexity. They shine for) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.50 Tf 0.120 0.120 0.140 rg 1 0 0 1 72.00 122.60 Tm (large systems and large teams. A small project is often better as a tidy monolith. Knowing WHEN to) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.50 Tf 0.120 0.120 0.140 rg 1 0 0 1 72.00 108.20 Tm (use each is the real skill.) Tj ET
